Description

Nutritious and delicious tacos filled with roasted butternut squash and black beans, topped with fresh avocado and lime!

Ingredients

  • butternut squash: 1 medium, peeled and diced
  • black beans: 1 can (15 oz), drained and rinsed
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • chili powder: 1 teaspoon
  • corn tortillas: 8
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lime: 1, cut into wedges
  • salt: to taste
